Package: WPD
Title: World Panel Data
Version: 0.0.8
Authors@R: 
    person("Benjamin", "Peeters", , "benjaminpeeters@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5095-2021"))
Description: What the package does (one paragraph).
    This package includes a comprehensive panel-data database (approximately 50MB). 
    The data is loaded on demand when using the function wp_data to minimize memory usage during normal package operation.
SystemRequirements: At least 100MB disk space for installation.
